{"tid":1828472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"BBC引述專家推算武漢新型冠狀病例或達1700宗","createTime":"2020-01-18T01:09:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-18T01:31:25.000Z","uid":263197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6c67279f53a6bc069fadd7e91ce7febe3892ec19","tid":1828472,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T01:09:48.000Z","msg":"來源：RTHK<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503474-20200118.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503474-20200118.htm&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKCvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=9627b0d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503474-20200118.htm&h=e376affa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503474-20200118.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n武漢新增4宗新型冠狀病毒感染的肺炎病例，當地目前累計45宗個案，其中兩人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n英國廣播公司引述倫敦帝國學院流行病學專家弗格森表示，根據現有數據，推算武漢可能有超過1700宗確診病例，疫情較公布的嚴重得多，對此感到擔心。<br />\n<br />\n弗格森表示，泰國及日本共有3宗確診個案，患者都是由武漢到當地，根據武漢機場每日1900萬人流及離境的3300名國際旅客，推算可能有近1700宗確診個案，認為應該擴大監測範圍，而根據沙士及中東呼吸綜合症的經驗，目前不應排除病毒人傳人的可能性。"},{"pid":"00979e64f5687a7395ab05f6d64bba126855c2bc","tid":1828472,"uid":65449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T01:14:28.000Z","msg":"香港懷疑案例仲多個武漢 一睇就知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48e1f77302866c747000d76cebab4db131e9595a","tid":1828472,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T01:15:36.000Z","msg":"傳到去日本泰國都有, 武漢點止得45單咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"652c16b83e4d94a89eb1fb37291593e9ffc92c05","tid":1828472,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T01:31:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}